title: American Horror Story Apocalypse Premiere Party
author: MaryGirl Moody
comment:
A few things I didn't mention during the live stream so I'll post them here, hoping to get your thoughts :)

1. There used to be a website for the fictional Westfield high that Ryan Murphy made. I was fortunate enough to actually see it before it was taken down. It had some information about it soon being shut down (Soon after Violet visits it)
The fact 10 Cloverfield Lane is playing before AHS 8 Apocalypse makes me wonder 🤔 I’m in California waiting for Premiere...

Season predictions; the big twist in episode six will reveal that the first half of the season was a vision of the worst case scenario between Cordelia and Billie Dean, the second half will focus on the coven confronting Constance and trying to prevent the rise of Michael. It’ll happen just before or immediately after Queenie checks into hotel. That could be why Cordelia sent Queenie to win money at the Price Is Right, just in case they needed the money to buy a ticket into one of the safe-houses
Unfortunately for us in australia who doesn’t have paid rv cant watch it until the DVD comes out grrr
The was way too long to be watchable for me if you want to do a 10 min review / reaction or recap that would probably get view
